<h1 align="center">📱 App Reviews Sentiment Analysis</h1>

<p align="center">
  Understand user sentiment using NLP 💬 | Visualize insights 📊 | Improve app experiences 🚀
</p>

---

## 🔍 About the Project

This project analyzes user reviews from the LinkedIn mobile app to uncover user sentiments using NLP and data visualization.

✨ It helps:
- Developers prioritize features
- Businesses monitor brand perception
- Product teams make data-driven decisions

---

## 🧰 Tech Stack

| Tool | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `Python` | Programming Language |
| `Pandas` | Data Handling |
| `Seaborn`, `Matplotlib` | Data Visualization |
| `TextBlob` | Sentiment Analysis |
| `WordCloud` | Visual Text Analysis |

---

## 📊 Key Features

✔️ Load and explore review data  
✔️ Visualize rating distributions  
✔️ Classify sentiment using polarity scores  
✔️ Compare sentiment vs rating  
✔️ Generate beautiful word clouds  

---

## ✨ Highlights

- 🔬 **702 LinkedIn reviews** analyzed
- 🧠 Sentiments: `Positive`, `Neutral`, `Negative`
- 🎨 Word Clouds for visual insights
- 📈 Clear plots showing rating-sentiment relationships

